What ever happened to professionalism and treat people how you want to be treated? Every time I leave this Starbucks I feel as if I burdened them by giving them my business. If you don't want to come in contact with people at your job maybe consider a new industry. A black coffee shouldn't take 25+ min. I will not be giving this location my business any longer.
